snippet.title: Arcade Longplay [719] The Pit
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: georgc3

A dig dug style game where you dig underground to retrieve hidden treasures. But you must avoid enemies from getting you and you must zap them if you run into them. You must make your way back to the ship before time runs out. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
